This is the sample code for 3D graphics and camera manipulations.
[ Code is used to explain basic hierarchy in various transformations and to explain camera properties ]

Useful Sources :
	http://www.opengl-tutorial.org/beginners-tutorials/tutorial-3-matrices/

Important :
	This code is in OpenGL's version 2.0
	For all further assignments version 3.0 is to be used!

Note :
	Makefile will work for both Mac and Linux.
	If it does not work on linux, use MakefileLinux
